name: Page Previous for WFH Tab

testSteps.description: 1: Page Previous for WFH Tab ({parentTab=Leave Management, childTab=View Request Status, tab=Work From Home})

children.description: Given User is logged into MIS
When User is on MIS Home Page
When User clicks on "View Request Status" sub tab of "Leave Management" tab
When Click on "Work From Home" tab
Then Click on Next button for "WFH History" tab
And Verify Records are present on Page
Then Click on Previous button for "WFH History" tab
And Verify Records are present on Page
